{"tid":2145322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞刺針 請0人都可以保就業？","createTime":"2020-08-08T03:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T04:26:40.000Z","uid":116309,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0915e90eabdf6627efd35563f80e0a54d39abc36","tid":2145322,"uid":116309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"【承諾請0個人點保就業？】<br />\n<br />\n幫僱主出糧的「保就業」計劃，第一期已審批近九成申請。當中有200幾間公司承諾請0人，夾埋攞咗900萬。呢啲「0人公司」究竟係咩一回事？點解請0人都攞到錢？《新聞刺針》去拍過門，發現有啲地址唔啱，有啲疑似執咗。除咗未知能否追回罰款，我哋仲還發現保就業計劃有其他漏洞&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #新聞刺針 ＃保就業計劃<br />\n<br />\n報料方式:<br />\nWhatsApp：66377858<br />\nFacebook Inbox：新聞刺針<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/newslancet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnewslancet&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=6f158e77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/newslancet</a>"},{"pid":"6f8bdccc0a0c72907466b5ad612d26f0c4466adb","tid":2145322,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"Link呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d066ea9d7f400404a993b7060ca333b560e0343","tid":2145322,"uid":128558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f8bdccc0a0c72907466b5ad612d26f0c4466adb","tid":2145322,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"Link呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=32306&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D32306%26ct%3D1&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=f44efb70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable